                             OPEN (world) MAP GEN

omg  allows  you  to generate a map for your open world game. manually tweak the
generated  map's  roads,  buildings, terrain, etc. to get yourself a great world
for your players to explore.

  - GPU Accelerated (powered by GLSL shaders)

[ PLANNED FEATURES ]
  [ ] generation of a landmass w/ a height map
  [ ] ui to specify properties (sea level, noise settings, etc.)
  [ ] ability to select city/growth center(s)
  [ ] generate dense, urban, suburban, and, rural areas
  [ ] generate roads between areas
  [ ] generate buildings between areas
  ...
